Upgrading this fork
===================

Schema and config migrations are documented in the README, under
"Upgrading & schema migrations":

    https://github.com/eilandert/ViMbAdmin#upgrading--schema-migrations

Short version: the panel migrates its own database — run

    ./bin/vimbtool.php -a maintenance.cli-schema-update

after pulling a newer version (the Docker image runs this automatically at
container start). See the README for the manual routes and the
application.ini config-migration notes.

(The old upstream wiki at opensolutions/ViMbAdmin is no longer maintained.)
